17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1009358, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "In a tradition from the Holy Prophet (s) it is said that the reward for reciting this Surah is equivalent to 10 times the number who are present in Arafah and Muzdalifa at the time of Hajj.Imam Jafar Sadiq (a) has said that those people who recite Surah Aadiyaat everyday will be counted from the companions of Ameerul Mu’mineen (a) and it has also been narrated that reciting this Surah daily carries the reward of reciting the entire Qur’an. If a person has many creditors, recitation of this Surah will help clear his debts. If recited by a person in fear, this Surah brings him to safety; if recited by a hungry person, it helps in his ?nding sustenance; if recited by a thirsty person, his thirst will be quenched.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Riwaayat mein hai keh Rasool-e-Khuda (s) ne farmaya, Surah Aadiyaat ki tilaawat ka sawaab, Hajj ke mauqe par tamaam log jo Arafah aur Muzdalifa mein jama hote hai unki tadaat se 10 guna ziyadah hai.Imam Jafar Sadiq (a) ne farmaya keh, woh log jo Surah Aadiyaat ki tilaawat rozaana (daily) karte hai, unka shumaar Ameerul Momeneen (a) ke as’haab mein hoga aur yeh bhi riwaayat mein hai keh is Surah ko rozaana padhne ka sawaab pura Qur’an padhne ka sawaab ke bara-bar hai.Agar koi shakhs bahot qarz-daar hai, to is Surah ki tilaawat ki madad se uska qarz adaa ho jaayega. Agar khouf ke aalam mein koi shakhs is Surah ko padhe to is se uski hifaazat hogi, Agar bhuke shakhs is ki tilaawat kare to usey madad haasil hogi apne rizq ko talaash karne mein, agar pyaasa shakhs is ki tilaawat kare to uski pyaas bujh jaayegi.", "UrduDescription": "امام جعفرصادقؑ فرماتے ہیں:پابندی سے سورۂ عادیات کی تلاوت کرنے والا روزِ قیامت حضرت علیؑ کےخاص صحابی میں شمار کیاجائے گاآپ کے ساتھ آپ کے ساتھیوں کے ساتھ رہے گا (مجمع البیان ج۱۰ص۴۲۱)۔ روایات میں آیاہے : جو شخص مسلسل یہ سورہ پڑھتا رہے تو وہ قیا مت میں امیر المومنینؑ کے ساتھ محشور ہو گا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15